<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Reechy" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Reechy,</orth> probably == smoky, and hence squalid, filthy, stinking: <cit><quote>Pharaoh's soldiers in the r. painting,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 3.3.143" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 3, 143</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>her r. neck,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 2.1.225" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 1, 225</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>r. kisses,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.4.184" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 4, 184</bibl></cit>.
